    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chairs with open backs and usually horizontal splats with the top rail and uprights rounded to give an overall balloon shape to the back.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
